  "body": "<!--NOTE: -->\r\n<!--- General questions should go to the discord chat instead of the issue tracker.-->\r\n\r\n**Describe the bug**\r\n\r\nWorking on https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/pull/2575 and due the bug fixed with https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/pull/2574 the validator client was using fork version 0x00000000 when the minimal is 0x00000001.\r\n\r\n**Expected behavior**\r\n\r\nWhen running the validator CLI with --preset minimal the fork must be 0x00000001.",
